text: Humayun Saeed (born 27 July 1971) is a Pakistani actor and producer. Saeed has appeared in Pakistani movies and dramas and earned Lux Style Awards, and ARY Film Awards. Primarily known as an actor, Saeed also runs the Six Sigma Plus media production house which produces television drama serials and commercial movies. Additionally, he has also worked in modeling and fashion designing. Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani actors
